<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zàn měi de gē shēng cóng zhè lǐ chàng xiǎng 迦南1338</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zàn měi de gē shēng cóng zhè lǐ chàng xiǎng dé jiù de lè gē huán rào wǒ shēn páng
 yé sū jī dū de hóng ēn shǐ wǒ men huān jù yī táng wǒ men de shēng mìng dōu biàn le yàng
 dà shān dī tián jiǔ xiǎo shān yǒu nǎi liú tǎng kǔ nán biàn chéng zhù fú shēng mìng huàn xīn zhuāng
 yǒu zhǔ jiù yǒu jiā yǒu jiā jiù yǒu liáng yǒu zhǔ jiù yǒu huó shuǐ yǒu zhǔ jiù yǒu fāng xiàng
 wǒ men tóng zàn měi quán de de dà jūn wáng zhǔ de jiù ēn chuán sì fāng chuán sì fāng</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1338</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>